Invited by the United Kingdom’s Ambassador to #Ethiopia H.E. Mr. Darren Welch (@DarrenWelchFCDO), #Burundi’s Ambassador H.E. @willynyamitwe attended a luncheon meeting with H.E. @HarrietLMathews, Director General Africa & the Americas at @FCDOGovUK (#UK). 

Together with other Diplomats from #Algeria, #Namibia, #Tanzania, #SouthAfrica, #Tunisa, and #Mozambique, they discussed issues of importance for #Africa, including best approaches to #SilencingTheGuns on the continent, #Agenda2063, implementation of #AfCFTA, etc.

